0010 REM "WOS - OP Code Calendar Change Maintnance"
0020 REM "Program WOM.FB"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0           |
